---
const tableOfContents = [
  { title: "What is an Xbox Gamertag?", anchor: "what-is-gamertag" },
  { title: "Classic vs Modern", anchor: "classic-vs-modern" },
  { title: "How the Generator Works", anchor: "how-generator-works" },
  { title: "Tips for a Great Tag", anchor: "tips-great-tag" },
  { title: "Naming Rules", anchor: "naming-rules" },
  { title: "How to Claim Your Gamertag", anchor: "claim-gamertag" }
];
---

<section class="bg-[#050505] py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12">

    <!-- Ad slot top -->
    <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-dashed border-[#1F2937] rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center mb-10">
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#4B5563] mb-3">Advertisement</p>
      <div class="bg-[#050505] rounded h-24 md:h-36"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Table of Contents -->
    <div class="bg-[#00D02B]/[0.03] border border-[#00D02B]/20 rounded-xl px-5 py-5 mb-12">

      <!-- TOC header -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-[#1F2937]">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
          <rect x="0" y="1" width="14" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B"/>
          <rect x="0" y="6" width="10" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B"/>
          <rect x="0" y="11" width="12" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#00D02B]">
          Table of Contents
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- TOC links -->
      <ol class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
        {tableOfContents.map((item, i) => (
          <li>
            <a
              href={`#${item.anchor}`}
              class="flex items-center gap-3 px-2.5 py-2 rounded  text-sm font-semibold text-[#94A3B8] no-underline transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.08] hover:text-[#00D02B]"
            >
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[#00D02B]/70 min-w-[22px]">
                {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
              </span>
              <span>{item.title}</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- Article body -->
    <div>

      <!-- H2 -->
      <h2 id="what-is-gamertag" class="scroll-mt-24 text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4 pb-2.5 border-b border-[#1F2937] leading-snug flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-block w-1 self-stretch bg-[#00D02B] rounded-sm shrink-0"></span>
        Types of Xbox Gamertags (The Gamertag Idea Factory)
      </h2>

      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Now that you know how Xbox gamertags work—and how to create one that actually says something about you—it's time to explore your options.
      </p>
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We've built a massive, organized library of gamertag ideas designed to match every kind of gamer vibe.
      </p>
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Whether you're going for something funny, dark, aesthetic, or inspired by your favorite anime or game genre, this isn't just about throwing words together—it's about finding a name that fits your style, your energy, and how you show up in-game.
      </p>

      <!-- Ad slot mid -->
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-dashed border-[#1F2937] rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center my-10">
        <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#4B5563] mb-3">Advertisement</p>
        <div class="bg-[#050505] rounded h-24 md:h-36"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- H3 -->
      <h3 id="classic-vs-modern" class="scroll-mt-24  text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-[#00D02B] mt-8 mb-3 leading-snug">
        By Style &amp; Vibe
      </h3>
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Go by how you want your name to feel:
      </p>

      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 mb-8 list-none p-0 m-0">
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Funny Xbox Gamertags:</span> From harmless memes to chaotic energy.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Dark Humour Xbox Gamertags:</span> For the edgelords among us.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Cool &amp; Stylish Xbox Gamertags:</span> Sleek, bold, and battle-ready.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Aesthetic &amp; Soft Gamertags:</span> Think cozy gamer-core meets Tumblr nostalgia.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">OG &amp; Classic Style Gamertags:</span> Clean, one-worders with legacy vibes.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Unique One-Word Gamertags:</span> Minimal. Memorable. Marketable.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Pro Gaming Names:</span> For when you're ready to compete—or fake it.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Gamertags for Streamers:</span> Built with brandability and cross-platform swagger.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Multiplatform Gamertags:</span> Great across Xbox, PS, Steam, and more.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Ad slot -->
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-dashed border-[#1F2937] rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center my-10">
        <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#4B5563] mb-3">Advertisement</p>
        <div class="bg-[#050505] rounded h-24 md:h-36"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- H3 -->
      <h3 id="how-generator-works" class="scroll-mt-24 text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-[#00D02B] mt-8 mb-3 leading-snug">
        By Identity
      </h3>
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Match your tag to your voice and vibe:
      </p>

      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 mb-8 list-none p-0 m-0">
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          Xbox Gamertags for Guys
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          Xbox Gamertags for Girls
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          Xbox Gamertags for Non-Binary or Gender-Neutral Individuals
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Ad slot -->
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-dashed border-[#1F2937] rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center my-10">
        <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#4B5563] mb-3">Advertisement</p>
        <div class="bg-[#050505] rounded h-24 md:h-36"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- H3 -->
      <h3 id="tips-great-tag" class="scroll-mt-24 text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-[#00D02B] mt-8 mb-3 leading-snug">
        By Interest or Theme
      </h3>
      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Dial in on what you love:
      </p>

      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 mb-8 list-none p-0 m-0">
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Anime-Inspired Xbox Gamertags:</span> From Naruto to Chainsaw Man fans.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Stoner &amp; Chill Xbox Gamertags:</span> Laid-back, vibey, and probably listening to lo-fi.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Gamertags by Game Genre (FPS, RPG, etc.):</span> Tailored to your playstyle.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Gamertags by Personality Trait:</span> Based on you—not just what you play.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Gamertag Themes (Fantasy, Retro, Mythology etc.):</span> Get creative with genre-inspired tags.
        </li>
        <li class="font-[Rajdhani] text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed px-3.5 py-2.5 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[#1F2937] border-l-[3px] border-l-[#00D02B] rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.04] hover:border-[#00D02B]/30">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Xbox Gamertags for Sports Fans:</span> Perfect for FIFA, 2K, and Madden junkies.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[15px] text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        No matter how niche or broad your taste is, there's a name set here to get the ideas flowing.
      </p>

      <!-- Placeholder anchors for remaining TOC items -->
      <div id="naming-rules" class="scroll-mt-24"></div>
      <div id="claim-gamertag" class="scroll-mt-24"></div>

      <!-- Ad slot bottom -->
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-dashed border-[#1F2937] rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center mt-10">
        <p class="font-[Rajdhani] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-[#4B5563] mb-3">Advertisement</p>
        <div class="bg-[#050505] rounded h-24 md:h-36"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>